        <section name="Overview">
            <p>
                These are the Scientific Research Software (SRS) maven projects of the 
                <a href="https://confluence.slac.stanford.edu/x/aowYBQ">Scientific Computing Applications (SCA) department</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
                We provide a set of web applications and java libraries for helping small and large scale projects manage their users, data handling, data processing and data visualization.
                These web applications are all experiment independent and easily customizable to meet the needs of our users.
            </p>
        </section>
    

    
    
